<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_247_r1l7">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> . Als Erhart Schüſtab vnd <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> volkmeir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l8">vnſer lıeb <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd Ratgeſellen nehſt cʒu Bamberg mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l9"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden geredt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . als ſie vns geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l10">Albrecht fürdrers vnſers burgers vnd ſeins leıpgdings wegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l11">das Erhat cʒu Meinpernheim / darümb auch derſelb <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l12">fürdrer <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> ſelber cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden kümt / Bıten vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l13">ewr <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc daʒ Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l14">darynne gnedıklıch <expan>beuolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſein laſſet durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l15">Alſo vvarcʒu Er recht habe daʒ Jm das <expan>onvercʒıeh<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> w </del> volg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_247_r1l16">Als vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_247" id="123v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als Erhart Schüstab und
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Volkmeir, unser lieb
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und ratgesellen, nehst czu Bamberg
                        mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden geredt
                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als sie uns gesagt
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, von Albrecht Fürdrers, unsers burgers,
                        und seins leipgdings wegen, das er hat czu Meinpernheim, darümb auch derselb
                                <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Fürdrer
                            <expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> selber czu
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden kümt, biten wir ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> etc., daz ir
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> burger darynne gnediklich
                                <expan>bevolh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein lasset durch
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n,</ex></expan> also warczu er recht habe, daz im das
                            <expan>on verczieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> volg, als wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> des wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
